reviewText:
Aashiqui.in Movie is directed by Shakhadeep and main roles in the movie are played by Ishaan Manhaas, Ankita Shrivastava, Dheeraj Miglani, Tiya Gandwani, Shubhi Ahuja, Deepan Shah, Sharmila Joshi, Priti Gandwani etc. Aashiqui.in is a modern day story revolving around relations on the internet. Aashiqui.in is a comedy romance movie and is expected to appeal to audience in metros

Despite being slandered, its not a bad film and is a good watch when a person has nothing better to do.
